headline: John Deere moving product testing jobs from Ankeny and Ottumwa plants in 2026
summary: John Deere has announced it will be moving some of its product testing jobs at Ankeny and Ottumwa to other facilities in a cost-saving move.

headline: Wall Street Analysts See Deere (DE) as a Buy: Should You Invest?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Deere (DE) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?
